title: Why aren't defenses playing defense, Giants offensive woes & Taran Killam
itunes:title: Why aren't defenses playing defense, Giants offensive woes & Taran Killam
description:
Dave Dameshek is finally back in Studio 66 with Maurice Jones-Drew to kibitz about Aaron Rodgers comeback on Monday Night Football (3:40), Giants offensive issues lately (9:58) and about MJD's pee-wee football team he coaches (14:40). Next, David Carr gives his Week 6 exit interview (19:22) to chat about why most defenses in the NFL are struggling (24:17) and if his brother was crying on the field (31:35)? Then, Taran Killam of ABC's Single Parents visited Studio 66 to talk about his favorite SNL cast members of all-time (46:50), his love for the Rams and he even did the 10 foot pole (50:25)!
